This patch fixes the Korean language resource file in Sikuli IDE 0.10.1.
Please follow the instruction below to apply the patch.

= Windows users =

1. unzip this package in the folder of Sikuli (e.g. C:\Program Files\Sikuli).
2. double click sikuli-0.10.1-ko-patch\patch-windows.bat to run it.


= Linux = 

1. unzip this package in the folder of Sikuli (e.g. ~/Sikuli).
2. cd into the unzipped folder: cd ~/Sikuli/sikuli-0.10.1-ko-patch
3. run the patch script: ./patch-linux.sh

= Mac OS X=

0. Assuming Sikuli is installed in /Applications/Sikuli-IDE.app 
1. unzip this package at anywhere, e.g. ~/Download/sikuli-0.10.1-ko-patch. 
2. open Terminal.app
3. type "cd ~/Download/sikuli-0.10.1-ko-patch" 
4. type "./patch-mac.sh" 
